```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Frontend as FastAPI Frontend<br/>(Port 3000)
    participant AIService as AI Service<br/>Flask (Port 8081)
    participant Backend as C++ Backend<br/>Crow (Port 8080)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL<br/>Database

    %% Initial Load
    User->>Frontend: Open /recommend page
    activate Frontend
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/tags
    activate Backend
    Backend->>DB: SELECT DISTINCT tags
    activate DB
    DB-->>Backend: All unique tags
    deactivate DB
    Backend-->>Frontend: ["python", "react", "ml", ...]
    deactivate Backend
    Frontend->>Backend: GET /api/courses
    activate Backend
    Backend-->>Frontend: 100 courses (cached)
    deactivate Backend
    Frontend-->>User: Display chatbot interface
    deactivate Frontend

    %% User describes goals
    User->>Frontend: Type: "I want to learn React"
    activate Frontend
    Frontend->>AIService: POST /api/extract-tags<br/>{description, availableTags}
    activate AIService
    AIService->>AIService: Call Groq LLM<br/>(llama-3.3-70b)
    AIService->>AIService: Validate tags against<br/>availableTags list
    AIService-->>Frontend: {domain: "Web Dev",<br/>level: "Beginner",<br/>tags: ["react", "javascript"]}
    deactivate AIService

    Frontend->>Frontend: Display extracted profile
    Frontend->>Backend: POST /api/recommendations<br/>{profile}
    activate Backend
    Backend->>Backend: GreedyRecommender<br/>makePlan()
    Backend->>Backend: Filter by domain
    Backend->>Backend: Score courses
    Backend->>Backend: Select with prereqs
    Backend->>DB: INSERT INTO plans, plan_steps
    activate DB
    DB-->>Backend: Plan saved
    deactivate DB
    Backend-->>Frontend: {steps: [...], totalHours: 120}
    deactivate Backend

    Frontend->>Frontend: Enrich with course details
    Frontend-->>User: Display step-by-step roadmap
    deactivate Frontend
```
